---
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 border-t border-slate-800/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Allt du behöver</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-400">Kraftfulla funktioner, enkel setup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">AI-driven sammanfattning</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">GPT-4o Vision förstår vad som visas — priser, knappar, text. Inte bara pixlar.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">Importance score (1-10)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Filtrera brus. Få bara notiser vid viktiga ändringar — pris, features, villkor.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">Slack, Teams & Discord</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Notiser direkt i kanalen ditt team redan använder. Plus PagerDuty, Jira och webhooks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">Schemalagd bevakning</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Varje timme, dag eller vecka. Du bestämmer. Vi kör i bakgrunden.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">Screenshot-historik</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Se exakt hur sidan såg ut för en dag, vecka eller månad sedan. Visuell tidslinje.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold">REST API & Webhooks</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Koppla till Zapier, Make, n8n eller bygg din egen integration. JSON-payload vid varje ändring.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
